@{i}Preprocessor Options@{ui}
     See @{"Options Controlling the Preprocessor" link "Preprocessor Options"}.
          -AQUESTION=ANSWER 
          -A-QUESTION[=ANSWER] 
          -C  -dD  -dI  -dM  -dN 
          -DMACRO[=DEFN]  -E  -H 
          -idirafter DIR 
          -include FILE  -imacros FILE 
